-- Virgin Blue Aims to Double Share of Corporate Market to 20%, Review Says
-- Sarah McDonald
-- 2010-06-28T21:15:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/virgin-blue-aims-to-double-share-of-corporate-market-to-20-review-says.html

          
          
             Virgin Blue Holdings Ltd. Chief
Executive John Borghetti wants to double the airline’s share of
the corporate market to 20 percent, the Australian Financial
Review reported, without saying where it got the information.
Borghetti has hired Jane McKeon, Qantas Airways Ltd.’s head of
government and international relations, the newspaper said.  
